\/hadith-on-itikaf-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":39720,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on I&#8217;tikaf: The Prophet&#8217;s spiritual retreat in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek spiritual retreat in the mosque\u00a0during the last ten nights of Ramadan, until Allah Almighty caused him to pass away. His wives continued to perform the retreat after him. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2026, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1172 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/last-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":39720,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last ten nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSearch for the Night of Decree in the odd nights among the last ten nights of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1169 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text